{"tid":1667740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好旭啲就屌鳩路人好嗎","createTime":"2019-10-21T15:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T17:10:17.000Z","uid":138812,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf0a9a564eed0dac71f522fc028ff20a77fee74","tid":1667740,"uid":138812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"我想講 係 我地出嚟抗爭為自己為手足做緊我地做得啱嘅野<br />\n但唔代表我地做嘅野對路人嚟講都係支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地搭黨鐵 我地最多咪叫人跳閘 唔好搭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔係屌鳩人傻西唔洗錢都要拍卡入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一來其實個幾蚊鏗嚟無意思（對路人嚟講）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢地本身唔係同路人係唔會做同我地相同立場嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌鳩人其實係好霸道好無理嘅事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先個位手足我驚你尷尬所以無講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望你睇到 亦都想其他手足留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非活動就做盡量翻好形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人會鍾意無啦啦比人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9e67c90034aa84d09e1c788d00f708eb50662d","tid":1667740,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"入閘唔拍卡唔代表出閘唔洗拍卡<br />\n出閘位都有foodpanda"},{"pid":"7c728df6dbe06bda5fbc3672a7bd546c416c96b0","tid":1667740,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"部份會燥底"},{"pid":"214a63fc87ecca68de70e7ec51ca82242a9f6ae7","tid":1667740,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"狗就係PR得唔好,手足請注意"},{"pid":"df7d0d36e2ed434aea0295fcfb16054754edafb8","tid":1667740,"uid":138812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9e67c90034aa84d09e1c788d00f